== How to enter flash mode ==
Fastboot mode is unavailable.
You can flash by dd from root shell.

Flash to recovery partition is recommended,
because key combination for recovery mode is unavailable.
You can boot postmarketOS by "adb reboot recovery" from normal boot mode.

